<i> food delivery</i>

04:01.149 --> 04:03.909
<i> and feed all</i>
<i> our friends here in...</i>

04:04.060 --> 04:05.410
[automated voice]
<i> "Spring-feld."</i>

04:07.823 --> 04:09.489
That's the excitement
I like to...

04:09.641 --> 04:10.916
Oh, we got a question.

04:11.143 --> 04:14.478
Wait, so one kitchen is
pretending to be 20 restaurants

04:14.571 --> 04:16.922
when it's actually
zero restaurants?

04:17.073 --> 04:19.483
It sounds like
you're catfishing the public.

04:19.501 --> 04:22.076
Think of it as
catfish po'boy-ing them,

04:22.096 --> 04:25.338
which is a special
at Mama Juju's Bayou Bistro.

04:25.491 --> 04:27.340
How much does this job pay?

04:27.493 --> 04:29.935
-Minimum wage.
-[overlapping grumbling]

04:30.086 --> 04:33.346
Plus overtime.
Sweet, juicy overtime.

04:33.499 --> 04:35.849
That'll replace
the newspaper in your wallet.

04:36.001 --> 04:37.851
And believe me,
this job's gonna be

04:38.003 --> 04:39.987
"easy peasy
like grilled cheesy."

04:41.340 --> 04:45.117
One Easy Peasy Grilled Cheesy.
That's you, Chef.

04:45.268 --> 04:48.936
Chef? [chuckles] Wow.
No one's ever called me--

04:49.031 --> 04:50.530
Make that 11 grilled cheeses.

04:50.682 --> 04:53.625
Six sushi burritos.
21 loaded churros.

04:53.852 --> 04:55.702
They're not stopping!

04:55.796 --> 04:57.779
Cheeses. I need cheeses.

04:57.798 --> 05:01.341
Cheesus, Allah, Buddha, Hashem.
We need 'em all, Chef.

05:03.787 --> 05:05.304
Hot stuff coming through, Chef.

05:05.531 --> 05:08.473
For the last time,
you're not my type, Chef.

05:08.700 --> 05:10.958
-Corner.
-Behind.

05:11.036 --> 05:13.553
-Under.
-Whoo. Over.

05:13.705 --> 05:16.148
-Betwixt.
-Ceiling.

05:16.299 --> 05:18.542
Baloney banh mi.
Veal lover's pizza.

05:18.635 --> 05:20.635
