grilled cheeses, Chef.

05:20.712 --> 05:23.989
Heard, Chef. Give me a sec.
I need mayo.

05:24.140 --> 05:26.325
-Ah!
-Please don't press charges.

05:26.476 --> 05:28.902
My parole officer's
trying to three-strike me

05:28.996 --> 05:30.887
instead of breaking up
with me like a man.

05:30.980 --> 05:33.498
It's fine. It's fine.
It's not deep.

05:34.726 --> 05:36.668
Oh. Where the hell's the mayo?

05:36.895 --> 05:38.486
Here's your mayo, Chef.

05:38.505 --> 05:42.582
Ah. This is Wing Hut on Super
Bowl Sunday all over again.

05:42.734 --> 05:46.994
