been going without me?

06:38.624 --> 06:41.382
Great. Tonight,
we're all making lasagna.

06:41.402 --> 06:43.810
You know, cooking as a family
has been kind of fun.

06:43.962 --> 06:44.811
Right, kids?

06:44.905 --> 06:46.463
Mm-hmm.

06:46.481 --> 06:50.224
