getting me through this.

06:53.321 --> 06:55.580
Love you so much. Bye.

06:56.750 --> 06:59.476
She's gone. It's GimmeChow time.

06:59.478 --> 07:01.327
I'm getting pizza,
pierogis, and paella.

07:01.422 --> 07:03.571
Fish-and-chips
and cake pops for me.

07:03.590 --> 07:06.332
Guys, we've been ordering
delivery for two months.

07:06.501 --> 07:09.076
