07:12.582 --> 07:14.933
Hey, hey, hey.
Bup-bup-bup-bup-bup.

07:15.160 --> 07:17.084
Let's not do anything rash.

07:17.179 --> 07:20.439
We'll totally cook
for ourselves, tomorrow.

07:20.590 --> 07:22.941
But we still need to eat
tonight, right?

07:23.134 --> 07:24.684
Indian food, maybe?

07:24.836 --> 07:27.595
Well, I am a little hungry.

07:27.614 --> 07:30.190
Tofu tikka masala.

07:30.342 --> 07:33.843
Mmm. Tofu tikka masala.

07:33.862 --> 07:36.455
Tofu tikka masala. Order up.

07:36.606 --> 07:39.516
Hey, hey, good news, gang.
Don't stop working.

07:39.534 --> 07:41.460
You guys have been
such rock stars,

07:41.628 --> 07:44.370
management is gifting you all
smartwatches.

07:44.523 --> 07:45.689
Apple Watches?

07:45.782 --> 07:48.133
Ankle watches. Monitors, really.

07:48.360 --> 07:50.026
They buzz and say stuff
to make sure

07:50.045 --> 07:53.597
you're always hustling
and a-grinding.

07:54.290 --> 07:55.307
[groans softly]

07:55.458 --> 07:58.201
Gil, did you have a chance
to ask payroll

07:58.294 --> 07:59.794
about our overtime?

07:59.813 --> 08:02.038
You know, Marge, I did.
Funny story.

08:02.131 --> 08:04.090
Turns out,
since you work past midnight,

08:04.151 --> 08:05.967
those hours count as a new day,

08:05.986 --> 08:07.802
so you won't be
getting overtime.

08:07.896 --> 08:10.155
That story's not funny at all.

08:10.306 --> 08:11.548
[ankle monitor voice]
<i> Rest detected.</i>

08:11.566 --> 08:13.975
<i> -Activating motivational zaps.</i>
-[buzzes]

08:14.069 --> 08:16.477
Ow! I'm moving, I'm moving.

08:16.497 --> 08:19.814
We work hard for that money,
and you're stealing it.

08:19.833 --> 08:22.075
Look, GimmeChow's
just a start-up,

08:22.227 --> 08:23.910
so money's really tight.

08:24.062 --> 08:25.337
You understand, right?

08:25.488 --> 08:26.730
[groans]

08:26.748 --> 08:29.007
GimmeChow? More like "holy cow"

08:29.158 --> 08:32.085
'cause their stock
just went through the roof.

08:32.179 --> 08:34.237
Ever since the pivot
to ghost kitchens,

08:34.256 --> 08:36.348
-this app is on fire.
-[alarm ringing]

08:36.499 --> 08:39.000
We've got GimmeChow CEO,
Finn Bon Id√©e,

08:39.094 --> 08:42.979
who, as of today, is the world's
newest billionaire.

08:44.099 --> 08:49.836
[coughs] Billionaire?

08:49.929 --> 08:51.596
I just work a lot harder

08:51.690 --> 08:53.598
than anybody else at GimmeChow.

08:53.617 --> 08:55.191
[Marge grunts]

08:55.285 --> 08:57.010
[crying]

08:57.028 --> 08:59.270
Mom, is everything okay?

08:59.364 --> 09:02.182
I'm fine, honey.
Just watching the man

09:02.200 --> 09:04.793
