here's my signed union card.

11:26.136 --> 11:27.602
We're with you, honey.

11:32.793 --> 11:34.216
[humming happily]

11:34.236 --> 11:36.569
[Marge]
Homie. Homie, guess what.

11:38.890 --> 11:42.057
We did it.
We started a union.

11:42.077 --> 11:44.302
Oh, that's, uh, great, honey.
[chuckles]

11:44.395 --> 11:46.137
That's great.
[belches]

11:46.139 --> 11:47.563
