<i> With his automated robots</i>
<i> destroyed,</i>

20:17.675 --> 20:21.068
<i> Finn Bonne Ide√© was forced</i>
<i> to hire union workers</i>

20:21.161 --> 20:23.904
<i> at a fair wage,</i>
<i> including overtime.</i>

20:23.923 --> 20:26.407
<i> Homer used his</i>
<i> GimmeChow gift cards</i>

20:26.425 --> 20:28.968
<i> to pay off the chicken's</i>
<i> medical expenses.</i>

